<color=Gold><b>Bone Knight</b></color>

<color=Red>(PRESTIGE CLASS: This class is not available at character creation and must be unlocked by meeting special requirements, listed below.)</color>

Bone Knights are patriots, living protectors who fight alongside the undead legions of their land. They provide tactical expertise and fine control to the legions of undead raised to defend their people. They serve as elite knights who travel abroad to complete missions that server the greater glory of their king. They wear suits of bonecraft armor that they craft themselves and learn to harness the power of necromancy, turning hordes of undead into disciplined, even cunning, troops.

<color=Gold>Requirements:</color>

<b>Alignment:</b> Lawful Good.
<b>Feats:</b> Smite Evil 2/day.
<b>Skills:</b> Craft Armor 6, Lore 6.
<b>Special:</b> Must not have any Champion of the Silver Flame levels.
<b>Spellcasting:</b> Level 2 Paladin spells.

<color=Gold>Class Features:</color>

- <b>Hit Die:</b> d10
- <b>Base Attack Bonus:</b> Medium.
- <b>High Saves:</b> Fort, Will.
- <b>Weapon Proficiencies:</b> All.
- <b>Armor Proficiencies:</b> All armor and shields (including Tower Shields).
- <b>Skill Points:</b> 2 + Int modifier.
- <b>Class Skills:</b> Concentration, Craft Weapon, Craft Armor, Diplomacy, Intimidate, Heal, Intimidate, Lore, Parry, and Tumble.

